         Powered by <a href="https://www.lemonsqueezy.com" class="hover:text-neutral-700 transition-colors">Lemon Squeezy, LLC.</a>
       </p>
     </div>
   </div>
 </div>
</footer>

<style>
 @media (max-width: 800px) {
   .hide-on-small {
     display: none;
   }
   
   .container {
     padding-left: 1rem;
